        the overlap zone: "FOR FOUNDERS" / "BUILDING FROM SCRATCH", matches brief exactly,
        not truncated). Title: TWO real text nodes 1:16444 "Entrepreneur-" / 1:16445
        "in-Residence" (both full strings straight from the node data regardless of the
        visual clip showing only "ntrepreneur-" / "-Residence" — real text nodes always
        carry their own complete `characters` string independent of any mask). Chips: the
        visible composite showed only fragments ("…20 FELLOWS A YEAR", "…+ SEED",
        "LAB RESIDENCY"); recovered FULL strings by downloading the raw content asset
        behind each chip's clip mask directly (bypassing get_design_context's
        already-mask-flattened preview image) and rendering it standalone — the underlying
