          chip 1:15867/1:15869 (asset content, viewBox 0 0 276.55×13.97) → "AROUND 20 FELLOWS A YEAR"
          chip 1:15890/1:15892 (viewBox 0 0 147.21×13.95) → "STIPEND + SEED"
          chip 1:15905/1:15907 (viewBox 0 0 146.33×13.97) → "LAB RESIDENCY" (already fully visible)
        Pill fill confirmed #F3F2EB (node 1:15868's own raw SVG path) — i.e. exactly
        `--color-cream`, navy text; these three chips sit in group 1:15862 (x764.96,
        entirely within O2's own unoccluded band x639.68-1172.8, confirming card membership
