          chip 1:15925/1:15927 (viewBox 0 0 167.09×13.97) → "8 TO 12 VENTURES" ("VENTU-RES")
          chip 1:15941/1:15943 (viewBox 0 0 147.76×13.96) → "SIX MONTHS" (already fully visible)
          chip 1:15957/1:15959 (viewBox 0 0 118.3×13.97) → "PILOT + CAPITAL" ("CAPITA-L")
        No body paragraph in the source (card frame 1:15781 has exactly 4 children: header
