        desktop as an absolutely-positioned nowrap 2-line label at those exact offsets:
        O3's opaque card covers the left overhang (like the source's mask edge at
        card-local 6.3, ±6px), O3's notch window reveals the "TED,/H-STAGE CAPITAL" band,
