        the desktop collage (≥1024): the composite shows NO numeral there, and rendering
        one would both diverge from the composite and overprint the source-positioned
        label. It shows in the <1024 unstacked layout, where each card presents its full
        readable pattern. (visibility, not display, so O4's header keeps the same flex
        height as the other cards' heads and the title row stays aligned.)
